text: Survivor Series (1992) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by the World Wrestling Federation (WWF). It took place on November 25, 1992 at the Richfield Coliseum in Richfield Township, Ohio. It was the sixth Survivor Series event held by the WWF. ==Matches== === Survivor Series elimination match === Eliminated Wrestler Eliminated by Method Time Beau Beverly Earthquake Pinfall 9:25 Typhoon Irwin R.
